OL,7,FScotland's drug deaths fell for the
OL,8,Ffirst time since 2013, but the number
OL,9,Fof fatalities was the second highest
OL,10,Fannual total on record, newly
OL,11,Freleased figures show.
OL,13,FAccording to data from National
OL,14,FRecords of Scotland (NRS), 1,330
OL,15,Fpeople in Scotland died from drug
OL,16,Fmisuse in 2021, 1% lower than in the
OL,17,Fprevious year when 1,339 people died
OL,18,Ffrom substance misuse, the highest on
OL,19,Frecord.
OL,3,CScotland's drug deaths down for first
OL,4,Ctime in eight years - but remain
OL,5,Csecond highest on record
